    ∇ r←{debug}JSON array;typ;ic;drop;ns;preserve;quote;qp;eval;t;n
    ⍝ JSONify namespaces/arrays with elements of rank>1
      :Access public shared
      debug←{6::⍵ ⋄ debug}0
