      :Trap debug↓0
          :If {(0∊⍴⍴⍵)∧0=≡⍵}array ⍝ simple?
              r←{⎕PP←34 ⋄ (2|⎕DR ⍵)⍲∨/b←'¯'=r←⍕⍵:r ⋄ (b/r)←'-' ⋄ r}array
